T02TD3508E:156b-1: a'arya dz'am gu l'i s'a dha nam /
T02TD3508E:156b-3: 'phags ma dug sel ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3508E:156b-4: 'phags ma dz'am gu l'i la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3508E:156b-5: sngon gsungs cho gas rang nyid kyi //
T02TD3508E:156b-6: snying gar dkyil 'khor dmar po la //
T02TD3508E:156b-7: dz'am yig las ni ye shes rdzogs //
T02TD3508E:156b-8: rig ma dug sel ma zhes bya //
T02TD3508E:156b-9: ser mo sprul gyi gdengs ka bdun //
T02TD3508E:156b-10: 'bar zhing g-yo ba'i nor bus brgyan //
T02TD3508E:156b-11: zhal gsum dang ni spyan gsum ma //
T02TD3508E:156b-12: gzhon nu ma yi mtshan nyid 'bar //
T02TD3508E:156b-13: khro bo dang bcas de bzhin du //
T02TD3508E:156b-14: sbrul gyi ske rags kyis brgyan ma //
T02TD3508E:156b-15: phyag drug rol pa'i stabs kyis bzhugs //
T02TD3508E:156b-16: mi bskyod pa ni dbu la bzhugs //
T02TD3508E:156b-17: phyag g-yas na ni rdo rje ste //
T02TD3508E:156b-18: gnyis pa dag na ral gri 'phyar //
T02TD3508E:156b-19: gsum pa gar gyi tshul dang ni //
T02TD3508E:156b-20: bdud rnams skrag mdzad mda' bsnams so //
T02TD3508E:156b-21: g-yon na sdigs mdzub zhags pa dang //
T02TD3508E:156b-22: gnyis pa dug gi me tog bsnams //
T02TD3508E:157a-2: me tog gis brgyan ske rags te //
T02TD3508E:157a-3: padma'i gdan gnas gser gyi mdog //
T02TD3508E:157a-5: dbang po'i mtshon cha spro zhing sprul //
T02TD3508E:157a-7: sangs rgyas sku tshogs 'phro ba yi //
T02TD3508E:157a-8: zla bum nyid kyi phyag rgya bsnams //
T02TD3508E:157a-9: dug gi rgyal la dbang bskur zhing //
T02TD3508E:157a-10: dz'am yig gis ni kha brgyan pa //
T02TD3508E:157a-11: dug gis 'gyel la sku gsum gyi //
T02TD3508E:157a-12: dug sel ma ni rtag tu bsgom //
T02TD3508E:157a-13: de bzhin 'di ni sgom byed na //
T02TD3508E:157a-14: ring por mi thogs byang chub 'thob //
T02TD3508E:157a-15: lag pa gnyis sprul gyi gdengs ka'i rnam pa ltar byas nas ;
T02TD3508E:157a-16: spyi bor gdengs ka gdugs lta bu rab tu sbyin pa ni dug sel ma'i phyag rgya'o //
T02TD3508E:157a-18: aom na ma:sha ba ra ka m'a ri ye tsutstsha'am tso da ts'i la tsutstsha la ya sam gha dha ni mitta m'a t'am gi aa da bid dhe aa he aom dz'a:sv'a h'a /
T02TD3508E:157a-19: 'phags mad gu sel ma'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
